00:39:35,620 --> 00:39:37,420
hundreds of thousands of years.

781
00:39:37,420 --> 00:39:43,340
And in recent research in modern-day Ghana, Larry

782
00:39:43,340 --> 00:39:47,500
Barham has discovered about 900,000-year-old tools that

