00:41:47,780 --> 00:41:51,700
And that takes a lot of planning, a lot of discussion,

821
00:41:51,700 --> 00:41:54,020
or a lot of skill.

822
00:41:54,020 --> 00:41:58,860
And many of the people who study the tools, a fairly wide

823
00:41:58,860 --> 00:42:02,980
consensus, is that level-wa tools can't be learned by

824
00:42:02,980 --> 00:42:04,020
imitation alone.

