00:42:04,020 --> 00:42:07,620
There has to be linguistic instruction when we get to

826
00:42:07,620 --> 00:42:09,740
this level of tool complexity.

827
00:42:09,740 --> 00:42:14,620
And these tools were, in fact, found as early as a million

828
00:42:14,620 --> 00:42:18,380
years ago tools that were made by the same process.

829
00:42:18,380 --> 00:42:20,820
Not everyone would call them by the same name, but they

830
00:42:20,820 --> 00:42:22,940
were made by the same process.

831
00:42:22,940 --> 00:42:25,460
So every tool that was made had to have various

832
00:42:25,460 --> 00:42:26,540
functional features.

833
00:42:26,540 --> 00:42:31,020
