00:42:56,500 --> 00:43:00,020
And we start to see some of this at the end of the

842
00:43:00,020 --> 00:43:00,980
Acheulean age.

843
00:43:00,980 --> 00:43:06,020
We see tools that are made a little bit more elaborately

