00:43:54,740 --> 00:43:56,580
But of course, we have no idea whether it was men who made

860
00:43:56,580 --> 00:43:58,660
the tools or women who made the tools.

861
00:43:58,660 --> 00:43:59,500
So we don't know.

862
00:43:59,500 --> 00:44:01,380
There was somebody who was probably showing off, but we

863
00:44:01,380 --> 00:44:02,940
don't know who was showing off.

864
00:44:02,940 --> 00:44:06,860
But then we find really interesting things about

865
00:44:06,860 --> 00:44:11,460
erectus that are difficult to explain.

