00:45:26,220 --> 00:45:27,220
They go into style.

888
00:45:27,220 --> 00:45:29,460
They represent one tradition over another.

889
00:45:29,460 --> 00:45:32,300
They're beyond icons and indexes.

890
00:45:32,300 --> 00:45:35,740
They're simultaneously indexes of task, icons of other

