00:46:41,900 --> 00:46:44,020
They produce what their culture needs.

919
00:46:44,020 --> 00:46:45,740
Their culture doesn't need numbers.

920
00:46:45,740 --> 00:46:47,740
They don't have numbers.

921
00:46:47,740 --> 00:46:50,180
And this has been verified with a lot of experiments over

922
00:46:50,180 --> 00:46:52,060
the years.

923
00:46:52,060 --> 00:46:56,220
So they also don't represent tense, but they don't have

924
00:46:56,220 --> 00:46:58,380
past tense or present tense or future tense.

