00:48:09,820 --> 00:48:13,420
Linguistic systems will have different rules, different

953
00:48:13,420 --> 00:48:16,300
structures, different constraints.

954
00:48:16,300 --> 00:48:21,140
So this shows that language has at least these major

955
00:48:21,140 --> 00:48:24,300
components, the objects, the ways they're interpreted, and

