00:48:41,220 --> 00:48:43,500
And these are add-ons to make things clear.

963
00:48:43,500 --> 00:48:46,740
It's not necessary to have this intuition to distinguish

964
00:48:46,740 --> 00:48:50,700
questions from statements, but it is very, very useful.

965
00:48:50,700 --> 00:48:53,780
In Piedah, like many of the world's languages, probably

