00:49:09,860 --> 00:49:13,460
And the word for hand is awe.

973
00:49:13,460 --> 00:49:21,300
So if I whistled it, and those are all very important in

974
00:49:21,300 --> 00:49:21,660
Piedah.

975
00:49:21,660 --> 00:49:24,540
So you've got to be able to hear those tonal distinctions.

