1324
01:07:50,780 --> 01:07:54,060
So there are all kinds of reasons that people disappear.

1325
01:07:55,060 --> 01:08:06,060
Hi.

1326
01:08:06,060 --> 01:08:07,700
You briefly said at the beginning

1327
01:08:07,700 --> 01:08:10,020
