1333
01:08:27,540 --> 01:08:29,580
We don't really know.

1334
01:08:29,580 --> 01:08:32,540
Some people, to come to Fitch would believe

1335
01:08:32,540 --> 01:08:36,460
that we almost certainly had, Homo erectus

1336
01:08:36,460 --> 01:08:38,980
