1352
01:09:20,100 --> 01:09:21,140
is human speech.

1353
01:09:21,140 --> 01:09:23,300
And with quantal vowels and modern speech,

1354
01:09:23,300 --> 01:09:25,500
we can communicate much more clearly,

1355
01:09:25,500 --> 01:09:28,500
but it's neither necessary nor sufficient to have language.

1356
01:09:33,500 --> 01:09:35,020
They could have produced sounds.

1357
01:09:35,020 --> 01:09:36,380
